          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "罪臣、杨延昭见驾，吾皇万岁！"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "朝前走不见了我的年迈父"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "往日里上金殿弟兄们成双摆对"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "凄惨惨悲切切把金殿来上"
        },
        {
          "character": "宋太宗",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "杨郡马为何不抬起头来？"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有罪不敢抬头。"
        },
        {
          "character": "宋太宗",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "恕卿无罪。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "谢万岁！"
        },
        {
          "character": "宋太宗",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "头顶何物？"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "御状。"
        },
        {
          "character": "宋太宗",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呈上来。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（杨延昭呈状，宋太宗看，念。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "宋太宗",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "“具叩阁人罪臣杨延昭，今告太师潘洪按兵不发，谋篡山河等……”"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵德芳",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唔！大胆杨郡马！别人可以告得，潘太师乃当今国丈，你都敢告？吃小王一锏！"
        },
        {
          "character": "宋太宗",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "皇儿，只要他告得有理。有道是：王子犯法，与庶民同罪。可以告得。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵德芳",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "可以告得？"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵德芳",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "杨郡马，万岁准告，你有什么冤枉？一一诉来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "容奏！"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "杨延昭跪金阶啼哭掉泪，"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "尊一声万岁爷和八贤君。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "听为臣一本一本奏当今："
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他要夺吾主爷锦绣乾坤。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "臣父子在马前做了先行。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "误了日期问典刑。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "赦却了父子戴罪立功。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "可怜他年迈之人气死边庭。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "黑煞日期要兴兵。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他要臣父子们将胡儿斩尽绝根。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "斩不尽杀不绝不许回营。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "围困在两狼山好不惨情。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "内无粮草外无救兵。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "潘太师提起了打子事情。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "射一百单三箭一命归阴。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他望子来子亦无音。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "可怜他年迈人李陵碑下丧残生。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "到如今只剩下为臣一人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "写下了御状叩明君。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "臣不告王子与龙孙；"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "臣不告文武众公卿；"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "臣不告各府州县共子民；"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "十道本告的是太师潘洪。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我这里写就了御状一纸"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那胡儿打来了连环战表"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "潘仁美在金殿挂了帅印"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在三关领兵来点卯"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "多亏了呼延将军把情讲"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一计不成把二计定"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "黄道日不发人和马"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "五百名校刀手把守关门上"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "要得胜许我们回营交令"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "臣父子只得决一死战"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "被番兵四下里围成铁桶"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "命七弟回大营搬兵取救"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将臣弟绑法标屈死可悯"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "臣的父两狼山望兵不到"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "命臣我探听七弟信"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "臣当初八个人把幽州闯"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "没奈何逃出了边关外"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "臣不告圣天子三宫六院"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "臣不告朝中公侯驸马"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "臣不告五府并六院"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "臣不告解粮官限误时刻"
        },
        {
          "character": "宋太宗",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "告他何来？"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "万岁！"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一告他私通辽邦打战表，"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二告他谋篡山河是真情；"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "四告他要臣父子做先行；"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "六告他上方宝剑乱斩人；"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "八告他害我父李陵碑下命归阴；"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "十告他卖官爵私受金银。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "情愿枭首在午门。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "杨延昭心中苦楚说不尽！"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三告他文官挂了武帅印"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "五告他逼得那呼延老将丧了命"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "七告他公报私仇射死我七弟"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "九告他在边关开怀畅饮"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "臣告他若有一事错"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵德芳",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "贤王听来也伤心。"
        },
        {
          "character": "宋太宗",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这是君也哭来，"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "万岁！"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我臣也哭，"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵德芳",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小王落泪，"
        },
        {
          "character": "大太监",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "两旁内侍臣大放悲声。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "万岁呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "万岁准了臣的本，"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "君是君来臣是臣。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "回到火塘为庶民。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（杨延昭下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "宋太宗",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "皇儿传旨：可有粗心胆大之臣，去到雁门关提拿潘洪进京问罪？"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵德芳",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "遵旨。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵德芳向内。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵德芳",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "万岁有旨：可有粗心大胆之臣，去到雁门关提拿潘洪进京问罪？"
        },
        {
          "character": "呼延必显",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呼必显愿往！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵德芳",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "启奏叔王：呼必显愿往。"
        },
        {
          "character": "宋太宗",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "随旨上殿！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵德芳",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "随旨上殿。"
        },
        {
          "character": "呼延必显",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "领旨！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（呼延必显上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "呼延必显",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "扫殿侯呼必显见驾，吾皇万岁！"
        },
        {
          "character": "宋太宗",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "平身。"
        },
        {
          "character": "呼延必显",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "万万岁！"
        },
        {
          "character": "呼延必显",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "贤爷千岁！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵德芳",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "平身。"
        },
        {
          "character": "呼延必显",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "千千岁！"
        },
        {
          "character": "宋太宗",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呼卿，命你去到雁门关提拿潘洪进京问罪，可有此胆量？"
        },
        {
          "character": "呼延必显",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小臣有此胆量。求万岁赐臣三道圣旨！"
        },
        {
          "character": "宋太宗",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哪三道圣旨？"
        },
        {
          "character": "呼延必显",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "头道圣旨：提上方宝剑。"
        },
        {
          "character": "宋太宗",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二？"
        },
        {
          "character": "呼延必显",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二道圣旨：发饷银十万犒赏三军。"
        },
        {
          "character": "宋太宗",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三？"
        },
        {
          "character": "呼延必显",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三道圣旨：后宫娘娘问候老太师金安。"
        },
        {
          "character": "宋太宗",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "件件依从。正是："
        },
        {
          "character": "宋太宗",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "圣旨到北番，"
        },
        {
          "character": "呼延必显",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "捉拿奸佞还。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵德芳",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "但愿多仔细，"
        },
        {
          "character": "呼延必显",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "贤爷！"
        },
        {
          "character": "呼延必显",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "臣知非等闲。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（呼延必显下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵德芳",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "朝事已毕，请驾回宫！"
        },
        {
          "character": "宋太宗",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "退班！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
